INFO 05-05 17:11:34 logger.py:37] Received request cmpl-97765b3d5d54416185468d62fc2272f2-0: prompt: 'I am trying to understand nutrition from the perspective of a university student writing an introductory essay. Please summarize the topic in a way that is accurate, accessible, and useful for decision making. The response should make room for how the issue affects ordinary daily life rather than only experts in relation to nutrition. Point out any common misconceptions that could lead to poor decisions. As part of the explanation, address how to make the explanation useful to someone who must make a decision in relation to nutrition. Also include a discussion of the role of geography, infrastructure, and access to resources in relation to nutrition. In addition, consider what kinds of institutions are most responsible for managing the issue in relation to nutrition.', params: SamplingParams(n=1, presence_penalty=0.0, frequency_penalty=0.0, repetition_penalty=1.0, temperature=0.0, top_p=1.0, top_k=-1, min_p=0.0, seed=None, stop=[], stop_token_ids=[], bad_words=[], include_stop_str_in_output=False, ignore_eos=False, max_tokens=128, min_tokens=0, logprobs=None, prompt_logprobs=None, skip_special_tokens=True, spaces_between_special_tokens=True, truncate_prompt_tokens=None, guided_decoding=None), prompt_token_ids: [1, 306, 626, 1811, 304, 2274, 18254, 29878, 654, 515, 278, 18520, 310, 263, 16372, 8368, 5007, 385, 22909, 2199, 706, 3686, 388, 29889, 3529, 19138, 675, 278, 11261, 297, 263, 982, 393, 338, 16232, 29892, 15579, 29892, 322, 5407, 363, 10608, 3907, 29889, 450, 2933, 881, 1207, 5716, 363, 920, 278, 2228, 6602, 29879, 15311, 14218, 2834, 3265, 1135, 871, 2902, 1372, 297, 8220, 304, 18254, 29878, 654, 29889, 8984, 714, 738, 3619, 3984, 535, 1441, 29879, 393, 1033, 3275, 304, 6460, 1602, 12112, 29889, 1094, 760, 310, 278, 8252, 29892, 3211, 920, 304, 1207, 278, 8252, 5407, 304, 4856, 1058, 1818, 1207, 263, 10608, 297, 8220, 304, 18254, 29878, 654, 29889, 3115, 3160