INFO 05-05 17:11:35 logger.py:37] Received request cmpl-7a0a3bae49e74b6ab09e09872f80eb80-0: prompt: 'Write a general-knowledge explanation about energy storage for a nonprofit volunteer comparing possible interventions. The response should be self-contained and should help the reader understand both the basic idea and its broader importance. Where appropriate, include what kinds of institutions are most responsible for managing the issue in relation to energy storage. Make the response useful for someone who needs both background knowledge and practical judgment. Also include a discussion of a case where good intentions can produce weak results in relation to energy storage. In addition, consider how the issue affects ordinary daily life rather than only experts in relation to energy storage. A useful answer should cover what information would be most important in a short presentation in relation to energy storage.', params: SamplingParams(n=1, presence_penalty=0.0, frequency_penalty=0.0, repetition_penalty=1.0, temperature=0.0, top_p=1.0, top_k=-1, min_p=0.0, seed=None, stop=[], stop_token_ids=[], bad_words=[], include_stop_str_in_output=False, ignore_eos=False, max_tokens=128, min_tokens=0, logprobs=None, prompt_logprobs=None, skip_special_tokens=True, spaces_between_special_tokens=True, truncate_prompt_tokens=None, guided_decoding=None), prompt_token_ids: [1, 14350, 263, 2498, 29899, 28385, 5485, 8252, 1048, 5864, 8635, 363, 263, 1661, 771, 9202, 27886, 261, 17420, 1950, 1006, 794, 1080, 29889, 450, 2933, 881, 367, 1583, 29899, 1285, 7114, 322, 881, 1371, 278, 9591, 2274, 1716, 278, 6996, 2969, 322, 967, 2545, 1664, 13500, 29889, 6804, 8210, 29892, 3160, 825, 17690, 310, 21561, 526, 1556, 14040, 363, 767, 6751, 278, 2228, 297, 8220, 304, 5864, 8635, 29889, 8561, 278, 2933, 5407, 363, 4856, 1058, 4225, 1716, 3239, 7134, 322, 15031, 24284, 29889, 3115, 3160, 263, 10679, 310, 263, 1206, 988, 1781, 7609, 1080, 508, 7738, 8062, 2582, 297, 8220, 304, 5864, 8635, 29889,