INFO 05-05 17:11:57 logger.py:37] Received request cmpl-73aadc060529488dac51700f1a35ddec-0: prompt: 'Provide a thoughtful explanation of waste management for a policymaker looking for practical implications rather than slogans. The goal is not just to define the term, but to show how the topic works in real situations. Also include a discussion of what an effective first step would look like for a small community in relation to waste management. Mention important uncertainties or limitations without making the response vague. A useful answer should cover the short-term effects people notice first in relation to waste management. To make the response more complete, include how success could be measured using practical indicators in relation to waste management. The explanation should not ignore a case where good intentions can produce weak results in relation to waste management.', params: SamplingParams(n=1, presence_penalty=0.0, frequency_penalty=0.0, repetition_penalty=1.0, temperature=0.0, top_p=1.0, top_k=-1, min_p=0.0, seed=None, stop=[], stop_token_ids=[], bad_words=[], include_stop_str_in_output=False, ignore_eos=False, max_tokens=128, min_tokens=0, logprobs=None, prompt_logprobs=None, skip_special_tokens=True, spaces_between_special_tokens=True, truncate_prompt_tokens=None, guided_decoding=None), prompt_token_ids: [1, 9133, 680, 263, 2714, 1319, 8252, 310, 19863, 10643, 363, 263, 13665, 962, 5790, 3063, 363, 15031, 2411, 5795, 3265, 1135, 269, 1188, 550, 29889, 450, 7306, 338, 451, 925, 304, 4529, 278, 1840, 29892, 541, 304, 1510, 920, 278, 11261, 1736, 297, 1855, 18845, 29889, 3115, 3160, 263, 10679, 310, 825, 385, 11828, 937, 4331, 723, 1106, 763, 363, 263, 2319, 7881, 297, 8220, 304, 19863, 10643, 29889, 341, 2509, 4100, 443, 6327, 2365, 583, 470, 27028, 1728, 3907, 278, 2933, 25160, 29889, 319, 5407, 1234, 881, 4612, 278, 3273, 29899, 8489, 9545, 2305, 8369, 937, 297, 8220, 304, 19863, 10643, 29889, 1763, 1207, 278, 2933, 901, 4866, 29892, 3160, 920, 255