INFO 05-05 17:12:30 logger.py:37] Received request cmpl-bf6c7784e81a4723a7ad3440d37d5c71-0: prompt: 'I need a well-organized answer about agriculture. Assume the reader is a parent trying to explain the idea to a teenager, and focus on clarity, examples, tradeoffs, and common misunderstandings. A reader would also benefit from understanding how the topic might look different in wealthy and low-resource settings in relation to agriculture. Suggest useful questions for further study at the end of the response. Where appropriate, include how data quality can shape the reliability of conclusions in relation to agriculture. As part of the explanation, address the difference between prevention, adaptation, and mitigation strategies in relation to agriculture. Also include a discussion of the short-term effects people notice first in relation to agriculture.', params: SamplingParams(n=1, presence_penalty=0.0, frequency_penalty=0.0, repetition_penalty=1.0, temperature=0.0, top_p=1.0, top_k=-1, min_p=0.0, seed=None, stop=[], stop_token_ids=[], bad_words=[], include_stop_str_in_output=False, ignore_eos=False, max_tokens=128, min_tokens=0, logprobs=None, prompt_logprobs=None, skip_special_tokens=True, spaces_between_special_tokens=True, truncate_prompt_tokens=None, guided_decoding=None), prompt_token_ids: [1, 306, 817, 263, 1532, 29899, 6388, 1891, 1234, 1048, 18032, 545, 29889, 22680, 278, 9591, 338, 263, 3847, 1811, 304, 5649, 278, 2969, 304, 263, 734, 264, 1875, 29892, 322, 8569, 373, 7542, 537, 29892, 6455, 29892, 11302, 22450, 29892, 322, 3619, 19818, 1689, 886, 29889, 319, 9591, 723, 884, 14169, 515, 8004, 920, 278, 11261, 1795, 1106, 1422, 297, 17173, 29891, 322, 4482, 29899, 10314, 6055, 297, 8220, 304, 18032, 545, 29889, 25589, 7118, 5407, 5155, 363, 4340, 6559, 472, 278, 1095, 310, 278, 2933, 29889, 6804, 8210, 29892, 3160, 920, 848, 11029, 508, 8267, 278, 12536, 3097, 310, 21204, 1080, 297, 8220, 304, 18032, 545, 29889, 1094, 760, 310, 278, 8252, 29892, 3211, 278, 4