INFO 05-05 17:12:55 logger.py:37] Received request cmpl-2819f8a3190147a7ae42c0098abae2da-0: prompt: 'I need a well-organized answer about supply chains. Assume the reader is a science communicator preparing a short public talk, and focus on clarity, examples, tradeoffs, and common misunderstandings. In addition, consider the tradeoffs between speed, fairness, affordability, and long-term durability in relation to supply chains. Be explicit about any assumptions used in the explanation. To make the response more complete, include the incentives that shape how people and institutions behave in relation to supply chains. The explanation should not ignore the difference between prevention, adaptation, and mitigation strategies in relation to supply chains. Please also examine why public trust matters when experts communicate about the topic in relation to supply chains.', params: SamplingParams(n=1, presence_penalty=0.0, frequency_penalty=0.0, repetition_penalty=1.0, temperature=0.0, top_p=1.0, top_k=-1, min_p=0.0, seed=None, stop=[], stop_token_ids=[], bad_words=[], include_stop_str_in_output=False, ignore_eos=False, max_tokens=128, min_tokens=0, logprobs=None, prompt_logprobs=None, skip_special_tokens=True, spaces_between_special_tokens=True, truncate_prompt_tokens=None, guided_decoding=None), prompt_token_ids: [1, 306, 817, 263, 1532, 29899, 6388, 1891, 1234, 1048, 11421, 521, 2708, 29889, 22680, 278, 9591, 338, 263, 10466, 7212, 1061, 10223, 292, 263, 3273, 970, 5193, 29892, 322, 8569, 373, 7542, 537, 29892, 6455, 29892, 11302, 22450, 29892, 322, 3619, 19818, 1689, 886, 29889, 512, 6124, 29892, 2050, 278, 11302, 22450, 1546, 6210, 29892, 6534, 2264, 29892, 21750, 3097, 29892, 322, 1472, 29899, 8489, 1411, 3097, 297, 8220, 304, 11421, 521, 2708, 29889, 1522, 6261, 1048, 738, 20813, 1304, 297, 278, 8252, 29889, 1763, 1207, 278, 2933, 901, 4866, 29892, 3160, 278, 297, 1760, 3145, 393, 8267, 920, 2305, 322, 21561, 23389, 297, 8220, 304, 11421, 521, 2708, 29889, 450, 825