INFO 05-05 17:14:58 logger.py:37] Received request cmpl-f8154212b95041079923d18b4a58dc1c-0: prompt: 'Provide a thoughtful explanation of cognitive science for a small business owner deciding how the topic affects daily operations. The goal is not just to define the term, but to show how the topic works in real situations. To make the response more complete, include what questions a skeptical audience would probably ask in relation to cognitive science. If multiple viewpoints exist, represent the strongest version of each before evaluating them. Please also examine the difference between what researchers know and what policymakers can implement in relation to cognitive science. Another important angle is what kinds of institutions are most responsible for managing the issue in relation to cognitive science. A balanced response should mention how private choices interact with public infrastructure in relation to cognitive science. Describe how the topic connects to everyday life as well as larger social systems. To avoid oversimplifying, include a real-world analogy that does not oversimplify the issue in relation to cognitive science. When developing the answer, connect this to the risks of ignoring the issue until it becomes more expensive to address in relation to cognitive science. A reader would also benefit from understanding a practical illustration of how data could be used responsibly in relation to cognitive science. Do not assume the reader already knows the technical vocabulary. Where appropriate, include the historical developments that made the issue more important over time in relation to cognitive science. Please emphasize clarity, accuracy, and balanced reasoning throughout the response.', params: SamplingParams(n=1, presence_penalty=0.0, frequency_penalty=0.0, repetition_penalty=1.0, temperature=0.0, top_p=1.0, top_k=-1, min_p=0.0, seed=None, stop=[], stop_token_ids=[], bad_words=[], include_stop_str_in_output=False, ignore_eos=False, max_tokens=256,