ned before discussing the details in relation to quantum computing. Please also examine what information would be most important in a short presentation in relation to quantum computing. Another important angle is a case where good intentions can produce weak results in relation to quantum computing. Where useful, compare individual actions with institutional or system-level changes. For practical context, discuss the role of technology compared with education, policy, and behavior change in relation to quantum computing. To avoid oversimplifying, include the main causes that created the current situation in relation to quantum computing. When developing the answer, connect this to why public trust matters when experts communicate about the topic in relation to quantum computing. Do not assume the reader already knows the technical vocabulary. The response should make room for how to explain the topic without relying on jargon in relation to quantum computing. Where appropriate, include the difference between what researchers know and what policymakers can implement in relation to quantum computing. The final response should help a reader understand the issue well enough to ask better follow-up questions.', params: SamplingParams(n=1, presence_penalty=0.0, frequency_penalty=0.0, repetition_penalty=1.0, temperature=0.0, top_p=1.0, top_k=-1, min_p=0.0, seed=None, stop=[], stop_token_ids=[], bad_words=[], include_stop_str_in_output=False, ignore_eos=False, max_tokens=512, min_tokens=0, logprobs=None, prompt_logprobs=None, skip_special_tokens=True, spaces_between_special_tokens=True, truncate_prompt_tokens=None, guided_decoding=None), prompt_token_ids: [1, 306, 817, 263, 1532, 29899, 6388, 1891, 1234, 1048, 12101, 20602, 29889, 22680, 278, 9591, 338, 263, 3847, 1811, 304, 5649, 278, 2969, 304, 263, 734, 264, 1875, 29892, 322, 8569, 373, 7542, 537, 29892, 6455, 29892, 11302, 22450, 29892, 322, 3619, 19818, 1689, 886, 29889, 3529, 884, 25917, 920, 278, 9545, 1163, 4822, 2