INFO 05-05 17:24:40 logger.py:37] Received request cmpl-7b6d4c66628342518e78006c8825cfdb-0: prompt: 'Provide a thoughtful explanation of materials science for a small business owner deciding how the topic affects daily operations. The goal is not just to define the term, but to show how the topic works in real situations. As part of the explanation, address why public trust matters when experts communicate about the topic in relation to materials science. End with the two or three most important takeaways a reader should remember. In addition, consider the difference between what researchers know and what policymakers can implement in relation to materials science. A useful answer should cover an example that connects the topic to science, economics, and public policy in relation to materials science. To make the response more complete, include the assumptions people often make when they first encounter the topic in relation to materials science. Suggest useful questions for further study at the end of the response. Please also examine how private choices interact with public infrastructure in relation to materials science. Another important angle is what questions a skeptical audience would probably ask in relation to materials science. A balanced response should mention the difference between prevention, adaptation, and mitigation strategies in relation to materials science. Keep the tone neutral, informative, and appropriate for an academic discussion. To avoid oversimplifying, include the technical constraints that make simple solutions difficult in relation to materials science. When developing the answer, connect this to a case where good intentions can produce weak results in relation to materials science. A reader would also benefit from understanding the unintended consequences that can appear when a solution is poorly designed in relation to materials science. Point out any common misconceptions that could lead to poor decisions. Where appropriate, include what kinds of institutions are most responsible for managing the issue in relation to materials science. As part of the explanation, address how to distinguish expert consensus from open debate in relation to materials science. Also include a discussion of ethical questions that appear once the topic is applied in practice in relation to materials science. Do not write a checklist; produce a coherent explanatory answer. A useful answer should cover the most realistic solutions available today in relation to materials science. To make the response more complete, include the role of geography, infrastructure, and access to resources in relation to materials science. The explanation should not ignore the long-term consequences that may be harder to observe immediately in relation to materials science. Mention important uncertainties or limitations without making the response vague. Another important angle is the incentives that shape how people and institutions behave in relation to materials science. A balanced response should mention the environmental, social, and economic drivers behind the problem in relation to materials science. Please keep the answer focused on explanation rather than persuasion.', params: SamplingParams(n=1, presence_penalty=0.0, frequency_penalty=0.0, repetition_penalty=1.0, temperature=0.0, top_p=1.0, top_k=-1, min_p=0.0, seed=None, stop=[], stop_token_ids=[], bad_words=[], include_stop_str_in_output=False, ignore_eos=False, max_tokens=512, min_tokens=0, logprobs=None, prompt_logprobs=None, skip_special_tokens=True, spaces_between_special_tokens=True, truncate_prompt_tokens=None, guided_decoding=None), prompt_token_ids: [1, 9133, 680, 263, 2714, 1319, 8252, 310, 17279, 10466, 363, 263, 2319, 5381, 12271, 1602, 4821, 920, 278, 11261, 6602, 29879, 14218, 6931, 29889, 450, 7306, 338, 451, 925, 304, 4529, 278, 1840, 29892, 541, 304, 1510, 920, 278, 11261, 1736, 297, 1855, 18845, 29889, 1094, 760, 310, 278, 8252, 29892, 3211, 2020, 970, 9311, 137